data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. Charming & Updated Corner Lot 3-bedroom, 2-bath home with a modern open floor plan and a versatile bonus room ideal for a 4th bedroom, office, or den. Stainless steel appliances, including a refrigerator with water/ice dispenser, range, over-the-range microwave, and dishwasher. Front-load washer and dryer included. Spacious backyard with a large shed for a workshop or storage, fenced-in for privacy and to keep your fur babies safe. Laminate flooring throughout with ceramic tile in the bathrooms. Bathroom surrounds are all tile! Roof 2017, and AC 2017.
